{"tid":1960141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送給李元元Lucy 一番說話","createTime":"2020-04-06T03:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:29:50.000Z","uid":220066,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37d0add4ad92bf2d6ae83b96d3439fdc7b306a54","tid":1960141,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"雖然你而家未長大成人<br />\n擁有一個正常人既判斷能力<br />\n但好快你會知道你老母當你係搖錢樹<br />\n未經你同意就隨便將你照片交係社交平台同人分享<br />\n甚至更逼你要應酬一班佢自己粉絲<br />\n他日你會明白你老母係一名藍絲<br />\n做任何野都係為自己利益而出發<br />\n甚至乎借你名氣而幫佢搵錢<br />\n希望你會長大後可以擺脫佢操控<br />\n<br />\n最重要你要懂得分別事非黑白<br />\n唔好受到你老母影響而做一個仆街既人<br />\n社會已經有好多不公義既事情發生<br />\n你老母仲係到說三道四<br />\n呢樣令人痛心，希望你成長之後可以獨當一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49243c3a73fe19fc9cc97407d2ac52907c998c60","tid":1960141,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66274004248d71b41631bba4407ca2d3b473b036","tid":1960141,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"881c38401ff3b49915683f9a544a00c0a1e50cd6","tid":1960141,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b8df2a0bf20b1fc850eeafa1873d22161fabb2a","tid":1960141,"uid":28059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:19:35.000Z","msg":"之前無follow 開 佢老母點藍法"},{"pid":"f782f260562d87d15f590fef2d27cc769c3d36da","tid":1960141,"uid":75394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"On9先喺ig follow d細佬<br />\n唔覺得意<br />\n睇吓貓狗好過"},{"pid":"c1375efda51b52715a5f01f05c198f9fda4e3ae4","tid":1960141,"uid":220066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts7BiJt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs7BiJt.png&h=b17baee6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https:/